<% content_for :head do %>
<style>
  body {
    background-color: #F7F6F6;
  }
</style>
<% end %>
<div class="col-md-6 hidden-xs">
  <div class="" style="background-image: url('<%= %>');"></div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12 side-pad">

  <div class="content padded innerpadding home">
    <div class="smaller paddinglol"><%= render "shared/logo" %></div>
    <div class="homehead paddinglol">Challenge the way </br> you travel</div>

    <div class="paddedi text-home">Tripin makes citytrips with your friends fun and exciting by giving you a list of challenges to complete.</div>

    <div class="verylilpad">
      <%= link_to "START A NEW TRIP",  new_team_path, class: "btn-main" %>
    </div>
    <%#= image_tag "tripin-illu-home.png", class: "img-home"%>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="smaller padicon"><%= render "shared/monkey" %></div>
      <div class="home-title">What type of challenges ?</div>
      <div class="text-home paddinglol">Let’s keep a bit of suspense…
        We will just tell you that the challenges will lead you to talk to local people, make crazy pictures, answer riddles… and of course, laugh a lot !</div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="smaller padicon littop"><%= render "shared/travel" %></div>
        <div class="home-title">How it works ?</div>
        <div class="text-home paddinglol">You just need to choose the city you are going to visit, pick your dates and travel buddies then you will get a list of challenges to accomplish.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="smaller littop padicon"><%= render "shared/passport" %></div>

        <div class="home-title">Can everyone participate ?</div>
        <div class="text-home paddinglol">Yes of course !
          Tripin especially is made for groups of friends and families.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="smaller littop padicon"><%= render "shared/photo" %></div>


          <div class="home-title">Is it free ?</div>
          <div class="text-home paddinglol">Of course, it’s totally free !</div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="smaller littop padicon"><%= render "shared/cocktail" %></div>

          <div class="home-title">What do I win ?</div>
          <div class="text-home paddinglol">When you succeed in accomplishing a challenge you can get free gifts or discounts at shops, museums, bars, restaurants and many other places !</br>Try it !</div>
        </div>

        <ul class="row littop innerpadding list-inline">

          <li><a style="color: #3b5998;" href="https://www.facebook.com/tripin.city"><i class="fa fa-3x fa-facebook" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li>
          <li><a style="color: #00aced;" href="https://www.instagram.com/tripincity"><i class="fa fa-3x fa-twitter" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li>

        </ul>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="home-title littop">Who are we ?</div>
          <div class="text-home paddinglol bottomshit">Two girls who love travelling and gaming. We are making this app to share our experiences and change the way we visit a country.</br>
            Don’t hesitate to contact us, give us advices or if you just want to say hello</div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>
